Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.49,Maihou,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gala Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get over there, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your candid opinion, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.49,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Holding back? What's that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure there's a distinction\Nbetween fortissimo and pianissimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And count all the rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wrinkle your brow when you play.\NYour posture's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't grit your teeth like you're in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The rhythm of your left hand keeps lagging.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are small,\Nso my fingers can't reach right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Play those notes by moving your wrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Play the first beat with your little finger,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then use that momentum\Nto take your wrist over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And move like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about changing the way you step\Non the pedal at measure 333?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That won't help me win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The score is impeccable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's God!\NWe are all servants serving God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was she always this kind of kid?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did her personality change?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not to play exactly how\Nthe score instructs you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is merely the selfishness\Nof someone who's forfeited victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just play with sincerity, give the performance\Nof your life with everything you've got.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The score isn't God.\NIt's not impeccable, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just an extremely emotional thing\Nthat humans created.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why it clings to you, like fetters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a cliché.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blurting out naïve drivel like that...\NNo wonder you fell to earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, I've got time before the lesson.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was just thinking that\N I hadn't heard your voice lately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, that's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should get her some sweets...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those canéles that you like so much...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not even mentally prepared for this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're always showing up unexpectedly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amnesia? Because you hit your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do beg your pardon.\NBut as I haven't seen you lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You never come to visit,\Nand the callous are easily forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to–
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Watari-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lying in wait for Watari-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was in the classroom just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am as kind-hearted as an angel.\NCallous though you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall give you a chance to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm appointing you as his substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you do have a spacious bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This cute one's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tug on my cute clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Adorable! The new one for fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adorable stationery!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with email?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so thrilled?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attention. We have a lost child...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't just ignore someone in need\Nwhen you come across one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:22.99,Twitch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Liar!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The mother was crying, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She must've been really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you shouldn't make\Nyour mom and dad cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That little girl... when I held her hand,\Nshe squeezed it really hard. So adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like she was saying,\N"Don't let go, no matter what!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she was scared that if I did let go,\Nshe'd be left behind, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've been making you\Nhold that all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uniform... So you came to school today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As it turned out, I was worrying for nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your school bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.30,Menacing,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seto
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't beat up the piano.\NKousei's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He just texted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with this, Ms. Seto?\NWith such irresponsible behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, you. You're always\Nturning on Kousei. Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I just don't want\Nto lose you to him, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what your angle is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if you ever put Kousei in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I can see he's loved, that Kousei Arima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,why did you take me as a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I thought it would\Ngive Kousei something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something other than sorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you can trust the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy? You're his enemy? Aren't you a\Nfellow musician following the same path?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, look how beautifully you drew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, show it to Nagi, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's had enough of sorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want Kousei to become a happy pianist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's so dark! Really creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving your bag at school\Nmeans double the trouble for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Over here, maybe?\NNo, maybe it's over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You lied?! Did you lie to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My bag isn't here at the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You didn't have it this afternoon, either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did come to school today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They let me out just for today. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to come here no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was starting to forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be sorry.\NYou should've had Watari, not a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it was your one day out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who explored the school grounds.\NThe girl you helped rescue a lost child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who snuck out\Nof the hospital and waited for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that I can live in their hearts forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The people here won't ever forget us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... won't forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget, even if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm glad it's you, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a little worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good, riding double on a school bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get in trouble if we get caught, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... about your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal. It's Hiroko-san, after all.\NShe'll forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a meaningless day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was such a wonderful day,\NI wish that time would just stop in its tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After shopping, and exploring the school at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the way back as a boy takes me home...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at how the stars are twinkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it because it's chilly out?\NThe words we exchange are so warm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It makes you seem all the more closer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be Watari's substitute or anything.\NForever... I want to stay like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't ask her the reason for those tears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow. The tempo starts lagging\Nbecause you're not playing it in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.20,Crash,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Annoyed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:21.15,Crash,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}Annoyed                    Annoyed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that's just what I'm doing.\NI'm playing it as fast as I can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't play it any faster!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So here's how you do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... Stupid machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play it like it's a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hate incompetent people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, let's just get\Nthis part out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I hate Kousei Arima even more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi! You dumped\NKamiyama-senpai, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many does that make?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.89,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assassination Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't stand\Nthe bookish, four-eyes type.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:13:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you decide what\Nyou're doing for the school festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The festival's in November.\NWe need to get on top of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're allowed to invite guests from\Noutside the school, right? Like graduates...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Miike-kun's bringing in someone famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei Arima... how am I gonna\Nmake those guys eat it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a hideous stench!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's reeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But our festival's known for its top students'\Nunique performances, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you'd be on fire\Nin that kind of situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Top students...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. I'm the angel\Nof Kurumi Junior High. And yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tengu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is he yelling at me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too fast. Your fingers are slipping\Nbecause you're trying to play it too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make it forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:13:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's your job, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are so small...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as Hiroko-san said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... sorry about that.\NUh, I've never taught anyone before, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a peace offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You think you can smooth things over\Nwith a sweet potato?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks really good.\NMelt-in-your-mouth good. It's a Beni-azuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I just cave in to a sweet potato?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you come here a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I used to play here all the time, years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With... my hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, Nagi! I'm gonna leave you behind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was the one who\Nstarted playing the piano first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I... followed in his footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he's obsessed with\N someone else besides me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, I feel lost now, and confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a dark labyrinth, deep inside my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want him to notice me.\NThat I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With my playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I telling him all this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of all people... The pianist that I hate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about ulterior motives, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most opportunities are, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I might have wanted somebody to drive it away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This obligation I feel\Ntowards playing the piano...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paper, rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-I-N-E-A-P-P-L-E!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paper, rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...scissors. Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't there anyone you're into, Arima-sensei?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Two in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nope, no one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}G-L-I-C-O!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're lying. There is someone...\NIt's written all over your face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of person is she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That can't be true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}C-H-O-C-O-L-A-T-E.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because she's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...a girl who's into a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a good enough excuse\Nto give up on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-L-I-C-O.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship over love, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How cliché.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... this is the best I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-H-O-C-O-L-A-T-E.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of person is she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This girl, see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's like a roller coaster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crying, laughing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's got me at her beck and call.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just by being around,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she transformed my\Nmonotone world into a colorful one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's a really dazzling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}really strong person...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Did you forget the canéles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So heartless! You promised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They were sold out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:31.20,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet Bean Jelly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I brought you some delectable sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, Watari-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, Arima is slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear he's teaching a first year girl piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce her to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that, Kashiwagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I told you, Tsubaki, it's not like\Nyou're an expert on the subtleties of girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You messing with me or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroko-san forced me to!\NI don't even want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A kiss mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one indulging in unsavory acts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kind of lessons\Nare you giving her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Kousei! Getting a jump on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you have time\Nto teach other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I told you, Hiroko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuses again! You can't afford\Nto be getting cozy with a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to do that,\Nthen how about practicing more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing my best teaching her.\NAnd when I get home, I do my own practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, that's not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting the time that you're teaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Other people are practicing more!\NYou just don't feel threatened, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm practicing enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then practice some more!\NThere's no such thing as enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The competitions are going to start up\Nin December, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you actually think\Nyou still have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before you know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that was some crazy mode I went into.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That trust of yours will soon plunge\Nto the bowels of the earth, Kousei Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did something nice happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of your playing, it's skipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you know sounds don't skip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you put it that way,\Nyou're right, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say, they're skipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's a girl who's into a friend of mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't see it happening\Nfor a useless wimp like him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way will things work out for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a little...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We might be just the tiniest bit alike.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pursuing someone we can never have\Nno matter how hard we try...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gazing at them...\Nburning with love for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I'm trying to destroy Kousei Arima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A noble sacrifice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A love that seeks nothing in return.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.31,Nameplate,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aiza
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're early, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am the phantom. The phantom who\N lurks in the opera house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot. Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been worrying about me, huh?\NAfter all, I was acting pretty weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not like her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bursting into laughter at the drop of a hat,\Nshrieking hysterically at trivial things,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}bursting into tears out of the blue,\Nturning so gentle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Giving up on something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone close to me was just like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's not like her... Not like her at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not true.{\i0}
